snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Facing YEARS Of Jail Time!
snippet.description:
A year prior, there were tales that Amber Heard may not be in Aquaman 2 as a result of the fight in court with her ex Johnny Depp. Presently, there are theories about the entertainer confronting conceivable prison time for a considerable length of time. Experts say that the entertainer may look however much three years in prison for faking her wounds to get a controlling request against her significant other. Johnny Depp sued the Mera-entertainer for slander over homegrown maltreatment charges, guaranteeing his significant other was a victimizer. It is asserted that Heard may really have faked her wounds to make it appear as though Depp was engaged with aggressive behavior at home to get a controlling request against him.
